00:12:30,790 --> 00:12:33,630
I don't want to be here.

285
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:34,910
Let Mother shop.

286
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:35,960
I'll play with you, okay?

287
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:39,440
Where's Mother?

288
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,360
Mother!

289
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,510
I'll play with you.

290
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,200
- Mother!
- All right!

291
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:50,510
I'll play with you, okay?

292
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:54,240
No! I want Mother!

293
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:56,550
Mother!

294
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,840
Why did you leave?

295
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,080
What a profound meaning.

296
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,120
Then I'll take this.

297
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,240
Sir, I'll go check out.

298
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,510
Sir, check my bracelet.

299
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,720
I think both styles complement you.

300
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:11,760
No! I want Mother!

301
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,320
Stop crying. I'll play with you.

302
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,320
Okay?

303
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,720
Lady, help yourself.

304
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:22,750
Okay.

305
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:28,360
Esteemed guest,

306
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,550
how may I assist?

307
00:13:30,790 --> 00:13:32,320
I want to customize a hibiscus hairpin.

308
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:33,750
Would Lady Mingshu

309
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:34,960
accept my order?

310
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:37,550
I'll ensure ample materials.

311
00:13:38,810 --> 00:13:40,080
Let's draft the design upstairs.

312
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:42,970
I want one.

313
00:13:42,970 --> 00:13:43,950
Give me one!

314
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:46,750
First, we do this.

315
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:48,840
Watch closely.

316
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:53,870
Amazing!

317
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,870
Whoever solves this puzzle

318
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,240
gets a pastry, okay?

319
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,080
- Okay!
- Okay!

320
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,080
Caught a chubby hand.

321
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,910
No eating yet.

322
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,270
Finish first.

323
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,670
It's him again.

324
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,670
Who are you?

325
00:15:10,670 --> 00:15:13,850
♪Two swallows dart
through the drizzle♪

326
00:15:14,110 --> 00:15:17,130
♪A lonely shadow
bars the window♪

327
00:15:18,110 --> 00:15:20,660
♪Thoughts lie concealed♪

328
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:24,480
♪With no one to talk to♪

329
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:28,750
♪Things will be changed♪

330
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:32,060
♪At least, I have your shoulders♪

331
00:15:32,810 --> 00:15:35,080
♪Always by my side♪

332
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,200
Don't go!

333
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:37,870
Don't go.

334
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,350
No, don't go!

335
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:49,910
Another dream.

336
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,440
He has bamboo on his sleeve.

337
00:16:10,150 --> 00:16:12,120
Mr. Lu, Lady Mingshu!

338
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:37,040
♪Only one petal left in the flower♪

339
00:16:39,470 --> 00:16:46,000
♪The wind scatters the past♪

340
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:51,200
Could it be him?

341
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:55,290
♪Flickering candles♪

342
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:59,110
♪Ignite thoughts♪

343
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:04,370
♪Fear fickle fate♪

344
00:17:04,690 --> 00:17:07,680
♪Chase moonlight in streams♪

345
00:17:07,970 --> 00:17:09,820
♪Any echoes♪

346
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:14,100
♪Drifting soul seeks home♪

347
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:18,770
♪Fear endless night♪

348
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:21,990
♪Tears and blades entangle♪

349
00:17:22,490 --> 00:17:24,050
♪Love and hate♪

350
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:30,380
♪Where to place them♪

351
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:35,200
Lady Mingshu.

352
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:43,560
The bamboo?

353
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:45,790
Your embroidery had bamboo.

354
00:17:47,830 --> 00:17:48,670
On the opening day,

355
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:50,750
I noticed your elegant bamboo design

356
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,720
and stitched it here.

357
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:09,950
Lady Mingshu,

358
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,000
are you okay?

359
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,680
Why didn't I realize it was you?

360
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,160
So the man in my dreams

361
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,960
is Song Qingzhao?

362
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:43,350
I mistook it.

363
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:47,350
Excellent.

364
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,480
Mr. Lu.

365
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:56,830
You admired bamboo,

366
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:58,960
so I sewed it

367
00:18:59,350 --> 00:19:00,350
on your clothes.

368
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,310
Was this merely

369
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:04,510
my wishful thinking?

370
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,560
Mr. Lu,

371
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:17,750
is something wrong?

372
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,720
My apologies.

373
00:19:28,030 --> 00:19:29,030
Mingshu!

374
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:31,110
Are you okay?

375
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:32,830
Are you ill?

376
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,480
No...

377
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,110
Then come out quickly.

378
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:37,550
There are guests out there.

379
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,880
Don't be rude.

380
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,200
Coming soon.

381
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:43,060
- Hurry up.
- Okay.

382
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:50,920
Come on, kids.

383
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,320
Eat while it's warm.

384
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:53,350
Thanks, Madam Zeng.

385
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:56,430
- Have a seat.
- Good morning!

386
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,760
- Morning, Madam Zeng.
- Morning.

387
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:58,720
Morning, Mr. Song.

388
00:19:59,040 --> 00:19:59,910
Morning, Mr. Ying.

389
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:00,870
Morning.

390
00:20:07,550 --> 00:20:08,390
Mr. Song.

391
00:20:08,700 --> 00:20:10,070
It's fine. Don't stand on ceremony.

392
00:20:10,070 --> 00:20:10,910
Sit down...

393
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:13,950
Eat!

394
00:20:15,030 --> 00:20:16,680
Madam Zeng's buns are divine.

395
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,350
Mingshu!

396
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:26,440
It's breakfast, Mingshu.

397
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,270
Coming, Mother!

398
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,160
Mr. Ying,

399
00:21:05,590 --> 00:21:07,510
can you switch seats with me?

400
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:09,920
I want to sit by Qingzhao.

401
00:21:31,110 --> 00:21:32,720
What did you call me?

402
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:37,000
After all this time,

403
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,200
Mr. Song

404
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:40,590
sounds distant.

405
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:43,630
Sister Mingshu,

406
00:21:43,820 --> 00:21:45,000
what's wrong with your voice?

407
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:46,350
Are you sick?

408
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,160
It's as soft as a kitten's.

409
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,350
Fine.

410
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:53,790
I'll call you Mingshu too.

411
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,110
What happened?

412
00:22:00,600 --> 00:22:01,830
Mr. Song, you came early this morning.

413
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,270
What's the urgency?

414
00:22:04,110 --> 00:22:04,950
Mr. Lu,

415
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,000
the triennial

416
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,920
capital Wine Tasting
approaches in a few days.

417
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:09,640
All spring exam candidates

418
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:10,550
will attend

419
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,920
to drink and compose poetry.

420
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:14,790
It's also an auspicious sign
for success.

421
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:17,070
Many elites will observe.

422
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,750
With your talent,

423
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:20,790
you'll surely shine.

424
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:21,880
Don't miss it.

425
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,720
Sounds like mere revelry.

426
00:22:24,520 --> 00:22:25,920
I've loathed crowds since childhood.

427
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:27,110
I'll pass.

428
00:22:28,110 --> 00:22:28,950
Qingzhao,

429
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,480
I'm interested.

430
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:31,320
Take me there.

431
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:33,430
Sure, yeah.

432
00:22:42,920 --> 00:22:44,270
I love bustle!

433
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:45,910
You must bring me.

434
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:47,340
How can I go if you won't take me?

435
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:48,350
Go.

436
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:49,520
Go there.

437
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:55,520
Buddy,

438
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:57,160
Lady Yuanying mentioned

439
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:59,240
that Jian Jinhai of Jian's Gold Shop

440
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,480
visited her father.

441
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:02,030
Could this be a clue?

442
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,790
I've already investigated this.

443
00:23:10,310 --> 00:23:11,150
It doesn't work.

444
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:14,680
But Jian Jinhai might know more.

445
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:15,520
Sister Mingshu,

446
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:17,110
follow your brother.

447
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:19,840
I'm done eating.

448
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,240
Take your time.

449
00:23:25,510 --> 00:23:26,920
What's wrong with him?

450
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:32,500
Well, Master Jian

451
00:23:33,510 --> 00:23:34,440
has already passed away.

452
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:44,200
Mr. Song has left.

453
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,430
Good.

454
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:52,000
You dislike Mingshu being with Mr. Song.

455
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,110
How did you know?

456
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:01,950
You...

457
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:03,830
You've carved "dislike"

458
00:24:04,350 --> 00:24:05,640
on your face.

459
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,440
The Song Family

460
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:09,270
would deeply vet our lineage

461
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,350
if marriage arose.

462
00:24:12,030 --> 00:24:13,310
Mingshu's secret

463
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:14,480
would surface.

464
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,110
Is that all?

465
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,750
Or is it because you can't let her go?

466
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,440
I'm just reminding you.

467
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:24,440
You chose

468
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,640
to make her your sister

469
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:27,480
for protection.

470
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:30,200
If she learns

471
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:32,510
of your unwanted feelings

472
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,790
and doubts her identity,

473
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:37,510
how will you explain?

474
00:24:38,750 --> 00:24:40,110
Mingshu has lost her family.

475
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,030
She's a poor kid.

476
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,350
As you can see,

477
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,720
she's having a great time now.

478
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,400
Meeting new friends

479
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:49,310
and having passion.

480
00:24:49,750 --> 00:24:51,030
I hope

481
00:24:51,750 --> 00:24:53,160
whatever you decide,

482
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:55,000
don't hurt her,

483
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:56,800
okay?

484
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,400
Rest assured, Mother.

485
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:07,720
I know what to do.

486
00:25:19,350 --> 00:25:20,190
Sister Mingshu.

487
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:21,870
What?

488
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:24,110
You seem normal now.

489
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,480
Why act coy

490
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,320
around Song Qingzhao?

491
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:31,550
I think I like him.

492
00:25:33,270 --> 00:25:34,480
How is that possible?

493
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:36,640
That bashfulness wasn't you.

494
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,550
If love stifles your true self,

495
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:39,640
what's the point?

496
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,000
Come here, listen.

497
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:49,350
You must guard your heart

498
00:25:50,110 --> 00:25:52,350
until after your brother's
spring exam success.

499
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,550
Then, as an official's kin,

500
00:25:54,730 --> 00:25:56,350
you'll have better prospects
of marriage.

501
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:57,750
Trust me.

502
00:25:57,750 --> 00:25:58,920
I won't lie.

503
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:01,590
You're right.

504
00:26:01,830 --> 00:26:04,270
Love should be free and genuine.

505
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,630
Sister Mingshu,

506
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:11,160
focus on the latter point!

507
00:26:11,590 --> 00:26:12,430
No...

508
00:26:28,350 --> 00:26:29,750
(Perhaps if you forget the past,)

509
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:31,830
(you'll find lasting happiness.)

510
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:34,590
(This Forgetfulness Box is for you.)

511
00:26:35,510 --> 00:26:37,750
(May it erase your sorrow and hatred.)

512
00:26:39,030 --> 00:26:40,240
(Bestow eternal joy on you.)

513
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,270
Flirting again!

514
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,960
How can a guardian

515
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:11,350
obsess over romance?

516
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:14,070
A true man shouldn't be love-bound.

517
00:27:15,590 --> 00:27:17,510
I'm sure you can sever attachments

518
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:20,480
and fulfill your duty.

519
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,150
Isn't it?

520
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:25,110
Yes. Teachable youth.

521
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,040
Go.

522
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,560
Guard well.

523
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:08,440
Slept soundly.

524
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:20,440
Buddy isn't studying in the yard.

525
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:22,030
Still abed?

526
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,280
Buddy!

527
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,830
Why aren't you up...?

528
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:56,070
I return to the academy.

529
00:28:57,250 --> 00:28:58,550
Take care of Mother and yourself.

530
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:02,030
The dressing box
holds heirlooms for women.

531
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:03,920
Keep them safe.

532
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,790
What an exquisite box.

533
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,720
This is forget-me-not?

534
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:18,110
So familiar.

535
00:29:22,210 --> 00:29:23,240
Thanks for your hard work.

536
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:25,940
(Renhe Winery)
I'll buy you drinks later.

537
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,480
Since Mr. Lu trusts us,

538
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:29,400
we'll protect his family.

539
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,040
Thank you very much.

540
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:33,240
Authorities patrol closely.

541
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:34,680
Lay low.

542
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,000
Boss, understood.

543
00:29:37,820 --> 00:29:40,900
(New Dawn)

544
00:29:49,270 --> 00:29:50,720
Buddy, I'll grind some ink for you.

545
00:29:51,270 --> 00:29:52,110
Good.

546
00:30:19,690 --> 00:30:22,240
♪May heaven and earth show mercy♪

547
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:24,780
♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

548
00:30:26,010 --> 00:30:28,530
♪As time quietly slips away♪

549
00:30:28,550 --> 00:30:31,550
Buddy, rest with some tea.

550
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:34,990
♪May this heart stay true
as the first day♪

551
00:30:34,990 --> 00:30:38,270
♪I'll wait through blooms and dew♪

552
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:43,820
♪Let greed and wrath fade with the wind♪

553
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:48,180
♪If all scenes fade to view♪

554
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:51,100
♪Will you return♪

555
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:54,180
♪Through years with sincere love♪

556
00:30:54,180 --> 00:30:57,340
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

557
00:30:57,620 --> 00:31:00,940
♪Counting endless nights♪

558
00:31:02,270 --> 00:31:03,200
(Mingshu,)

559
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:05,310
(I seem)

560
00:31:06,550 --> 00:31:08,160
(to be holding on to you
more and more tightly.)

561
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:11,140
♪If the moon above the sea is full♪

562
00:31:11,420 --> 00:31:14,220
♪Will you return♪

563
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:17,500
♪In years left, wait for me♪

564
00:31:17,660 --> 00:31:20,620
♪With a beginning and an end♪

565
00:31:20,900 --> 00:31:23,900
♪May time inscribe our names♪

566
00:31:24,180 --> 00:31:27,060
♪Where vows remain♪

567
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:29,940
♪As if it were yesterday♪

568
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,110
Food, drink and relationships

569
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:33,480
are the great desires inherent
in human nature.

570
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:35,960
Death and poverty

571
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:38,180
are the great aversions
in the human heart.

572
00:31:38,570 --> 00:31:39,590
Therefore, desire and aversion

573
00:31:40,250 --> 00:31:41,550
form the fundamental axes
of the mind.

574
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,700
(Book of Rites)
People remain hidden

575
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:44,830
and can't be fully fathomed.

576
00:31:45,830 --> 00:31:47,130
Both virtue and vice dwell in the heart,

