604
00:33:31,110 --> 00:33:32,440
The intricacies of these matters

605
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:34,440
require your own discernment.

606
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:38,310
I shall remember

607
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,640
your teachings, Mother.

608
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,240
Alright,

