00:34:36,760 --> 00:34:37,670
Let me

615
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:40,230
remind you.

616
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,320
Wherever you may go

617
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:45,510
hereafter,

618
00:34:46,030 --> 00:34:46,870
