619
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:48,510
without fear

620
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:49,840
or worry.

621
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,000
Our parental hearts

622
00:34:52,510 --> 00:34:55,320
