00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:54,930
♪At least, I have your shoulders♪

633
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:57,840
♪Always by my side♪

634
00:35:58,610 --> 00:36:01,890
♪Shining bright as fireflies♪

635
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,510
Consort, Prince Rui approaches.

636
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,880
Quick! Sit properly.

637
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,760
Probably patrolling guards.

638
00:36:36,230 --> 00:36:37,510
Prince Rui remains in his study?

639
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:38,960
I'll investigate.

640
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,670
The lamp still burns
in Prince Rui's study.

641
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:49,800
Consort,

642
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,760
would he truly not come?

643
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:53,710
This is your wedding night.

644
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:55,470
I'll wait for one incense stick's time.

645
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,840
If he fails to appear,

646
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:57,920
I'll summon him myself.

647
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:00,480
You'd go yourself?

648
00:37:00,610 --> 00:37:02,920
Do you think there are no palace spies
watching this house?

649
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:04,360
On his wedding night,

650
00:37:04,590 --> 00:37:06,400
he must stay in the chamber.

651
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:08,070
After tonight,

652
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,120
I'd prefer him not to come.

653
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:32,510
Your Highness, the Hai hour will pass.
