661
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:54,510
Nagging.

662
00:38:17,710 --> 00:38:18,670
He's coming!

663
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:20,030
Truly approaching this time.

664
00:38:20,210 --> 00:38:21,070
Really?

665
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:21,910
Yeah.

666
00:38:22,030 --> 00:38:23,550
Lady, no, Consort.

667
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,110
Quickly! The fan.

