672
00:38:43,710 --> 00:38:44,550
Perhaps

673
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:46,030
drink some wine for courage?

674
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,960
Fetch it swiftly!

675
00:38:53,370 --> 00:38:54,240
Hurry up!

676
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,760
Okay, I'll be right there.

677
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:05,950
Here.

678
00:39:08,590 --> 00:39:10,630
Prince Rui arrives!

679
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:20,880
Prince Rui.

680
00:40:00,230 --> 00:40:01,070
Nervous?

681
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:05,000
Please retrieve another cup.

682
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,760
This cross-cupped wine

683
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:27,480
