686
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:36,120
Very well.

687
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:37,890
Since you disregard etiquette,

688
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:39,190
I needn't observe

689
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,760
the fan-removal ritual.

690
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:47,000
If Your Highness insists,

691
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:49,280
I'll obey.

692
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:17,320
The Zi hour approaches.
