709
00:41:54,310 --> 00:41:56,550
I trust Your Highness won't recant.

710
00:41:57,670 --> 00:41:58,510
Of course not.

711
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:01,480
I'll obey.

712
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:39,360
I shall retire first.

713
00:42:39,700 --> 00:42:41,130
Your Highness,
